♪ It's a dark season ♪

20:04.616 --> 20:06.884
♪ And it's been all along ♪

20:06.885 --> 20:09.152
♪ A grim season ♪

20:09.153 --> 20:12.188
♪ There's no point in pretending ♪

20:15.260 --> 20:17.294
♪ For some reason ♪

20:17.295 --> 20:19.663
♪ We're still singing this song ♪

20:19.664 --> 20:24.101
♪ But this time with a
d'doozy of an ending ♪

20:24.102 --> 20:25.235
- What just happened?
- What?

20:25.236 --> 20:27.470
- I thought...
- Oh, look, a squirrel!

20:31.075 --> 20:33.010
♪ Now I must ride to... Somewhere ♪

20:33.011 --> 20:37.347
♪ To do something to atone ♪

20:37.348 --> 20:41.518
♪ I'll cross the lonely sea
to spend my lonely life alone ♪

20:41.519 --> 20:43.654
♪ Beyond the bitter desert ♪

20:43.655 --> 20:46.023
♪ In the shadow of mount spinster ♪

20:46.024 --> 20:47.624
